Racket Language (formerly PLT Scheme) bindings to libtcod

The current bindings are updated to the svn version of libtcod, which means
they do not work with the 1.5.0 version!

In order to run tests, you need to create a symlink to the data dir within the
libtcod in order to load a font.

libtcod homepage: http://doryen.eptalys.net/libtcod/
